<http://dx.doi.org/10.11646/zootaxa.4099.1.1>
    dc:creator "François Génier; Patrick Arnaud" ;
    dc:date "2016" ;
    dc:title "Dendropaemon Perty, 1830: taxonomy, systematics and phylogeny of the morphologically most derived phanaeine genus (Coleoptera: Scarabaeidae, Scarabaeinae, Phanaeini)" ;
    fabio:hasPart <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.268277> .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.268277>
    dc:description "FIGURES 13 – 18. Dorsal habitus. 13. D. angustulus, male holotype; 14. D. ater, male neotype; 15. D. flechtmanni, male holotype; 16. D. larseni, male holotype; 17. D. piceus, male holotype; 18. D. telephus, male holotype." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/268277/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

